## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- [Bun](https://bun.sh/) runtime
{{#if includeDb}}
- PostgreSQL database
{{/if}}

### Installation

```bash
bun install
```

### Development

```bash
bun run dev
```

The service will start at `http://localhost:3000`.

### Building

```bash
bun run build
```

### Running in Production

```bash
bun run start
```

## API Endpoints

### Health Check

- `GET /health` - Service health status
- `GET /health/ready` - Readiness check
- `GET /health/live` - Liveness check

