## Database

This service uses Drizzle ORM with PostgreSQL.

### Migrations

```bash
bun run drizzle-kit generate:pg
bun run drizzle-kit push:pg
```

### Environment Variables

- `DATABASE_URL` - PostgreSQL connection string
